{"tid":415013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"864億元建高鐵 運房局認無法收回成本","createTime":"2017-09-26T15:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T16:06:21.000Z","uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"835ca6d5d2c904150488f412c534468179526870","tid":415013,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段目標訂於明年第三季通車，目前政府正與港鐵公司商討高鐵的營運安排。運輸及房屋局向立法會提交文件稱，最快今年12月將營運高鐵所需的土地，以象徵式地價1000元租予九鐵公司，並每年收取相當於應課差餉租值3%的地租，年期為50年；九鐵公司會再將高鐵交給港鐵公司營運。但政府表明有關安排將不能收回高鐵的興建成本。<br />\n<br />\n運房局提交文件交代高鐵香港段的土地及資產擁有安排，指當局早於2009年表明，高鐵香港段建成後，政府可以象徵式費用將高鐵租予九鐵公司，讓九鐵公司把高鐵納入與港鐵公司簽訂的《服務經營權協議》。<br />\n<br />\n當局稱，至今「這個立場沒有改變的理由」，而且政府一早已公開表明有關意向，故毋須進行公眾諮詢，遂建議根據《九廣鐵路公司條例》，將營運高鐵所需的土地及土地權益，包括全長26公里的行車隧道及鐵路系統、石崗列車停放處及緊急救援站、沿線的通風樓及緊急救援出入口等，歸屬九鐵公司，為期50年。<br />\n<br />\n當局續稱，會向九鐵公司收取象徵式地價1000元，以及每年收取相當於應課差餉租值3%的地租；再由兩鐵合併時已簽訂的《服務經營權協議》，九鐵公司將高鐵香港段的服務經營權交予港鐵公司，港鐵將負責高鐵的營運及維修保養，而九鐵期間可向港鐵收取服務經營費；港鐵亦「應於2017年12月前正式獲委任為高鐵的營辦商」。當局指，政府有意加設終止條款，使政府有權在有需要下，收回營運高鐵所需的土地。<br />\n<br />\n不過，當局承認，在有關安排下，政府將不能收回高鐵整體合計864.2億元的建設成本，但就指只要高鐵營運業務時獲得盈利，政府仍可從九鐵公司獲得紅利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506414080829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506414080829&d=xGs9AEHpjal4PHFOuyzWgZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a6a0f5cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506414080829&h=3006e9ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506414080829</a>"},{"pid":"14ed07d79f28aeb9bc12ade20eb3756bbf2f0aa8","tid":415013,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170926/s00001/6565d5ec05f88eab0c91b23d561ddacc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F6565d5ec05f88eab0c91b23d561ddacc.jpg&h=810c3447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1af54004e86aee4ee179ac0ed534e95c43ecdde7","tid":415013,"uid":1482,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"駛撚佢認 全香港都知既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54834a2ae0b286595e7edea0ff34f1f39ea60bf0","tid":415013,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駛撚佢認 全香港都知既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d19e4e94ea031e4652fdd19c404179b97a445805","tid":415013,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"街知巷聞"},{"pid":"b08c3cc2e16e413595343dfb403f4cf79b3c052a","tid":415013,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:51:30.000Z","msg":"CLS！"},{"pid":"b49c54a7399131339f071ebcd8fabff0b50c9e0b","tid":415013,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"派晒囉"},{"pid":"e2663698bbf2c467e0f5e53e1e02f0470ead0eda","tid":415013,"uid":103237,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"有冇方法捉番鄭汝樺出黎屌?<br />\n<br />\n過左骨就扮唔知"},{"pid":"bf7be9af346ee8605be37a3522a4932056900a66","tid":415013,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"繼續超支嘛, 896.4億咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acecf18f4c5b327647e60e16c9577a986a57c07","tid":415013,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"一早講左啦"},{"pid":"83b3508179d325d77995a8d4879990bed2e23490","tid":415013,"uid":522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇方法捉番鄭汝樺出黎屌?<br />\n<br />\n過左骨就扮唔知</blockquote><br />\n建國後清算名單"},{"pid":"c227f90ac200d63fb9e3efaefc47c2278589db76","tid":415013,"uid":53687,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲衰嘢CCTVB實唔會報，<br />\n大家積極啲落街唱佢，唔好掛住上網圍爐。"},{"pid":"cc62625a4d8d49e427f0055bcf417ffb022cce51","tid":415013,"uid":91633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"要起個時咩都得唔會超支成本可以收番<br />\n都未起好已經係咁超支成本又收唔番<br />\n正仆街港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83addda192e637f69e6ce81cac933ca0442a5ae0","tid":415013,"uid":83582,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/22/Stopxrl_%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%A2%91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F22%2FStopxrl_%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E7%25A2%2591.jpg&h=bfd2ff36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a458fb5979ecf2dfc1c8c300820431259e7d4","tid":415013,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"起完先認<br />\n你吹呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051e8c07f9044d3b2458faf683bac27dd5b3b4fd","tid":415013,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">指政府估算保守 工程界盧偉國：如這樣，根本毋須高鐵</span><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段「一地兩檢」爭論持續，工程界立法會議員盧偉國與公民黨議員陳淑莊對談時，指政府的高鐵客流估算「相當相當保守」，直言「如果這樣，根本不需要搞這麼大投資的高鐵香港段，港深直通車就是了」。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉國與本身是「一地兩檢」關注組召集人的陳淑莊，早上於商台節目討論「一地兩檢」問題。盧偉國稱，如果將來西九總站目標是成為「重要樞紐」，唯一方法是在西九龍站進行「一地兩檢」，這亦是高鐵設計上有15個月台的原因。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，關注組提出的「內地一地兩檢」方案，對赴內地或來港旅客都不是最佳方案，「如果能在西九總站通了關，（乘客）完全自由駁去哪裏，途中想下車都行」。<br />\n<br />\n不過陳淑莊質疑高鐵香港段成為「重要樞紐」的可能性，又引述政府文件稱，預計十多年後大部分高鐵乘客仍是短途客，「八成都是短途」。<span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉國</span>隨即反駁，認為政府估算「相當相當保守」，更<span style=\"color: red;\">直言「如果這樣，根本不需要搞這麼大投資的高鐵香港段，港深直通車就是了」</span>，故「樞紐<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應該</span></span>是目標」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳淑莊形容關注組像被政府「孤立了」，舉例指關注組曾多次邀請司局長討論，但都被拒絕及冷待，「暫時都是當我們透明，(令人感到)失望」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506392716857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506392716857&d=xGs9AEHpjal4PHFOuyzWgZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=46a9502d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506392716857&h=b9427998\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506392716857</a>"},{"pid":"fb432a3f30d2787424872180198a4bee01200ee8","tid":415013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，陳淑莊形容關注組像被政府「孤立了」，舉例指關注組曾多次邀請司局長討論，但都被拒絕及冷待，「暫時都是當我們透明，(令人感到)失望」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺明啦！<br />\n<br />\n咁你和理非又奈得佢乜何？"},{"pid":"0db8c8a23ce210357c9002e6bb85f83f5a356f36","tid":415013,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"兩岸罵聲停不住，高鐵已過萬重山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d8a3d847e4d5a6ffaca3b1726486af9942076","tid":415013,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n不過，當局承認，在有關安排下，政府將不能收回高鐵整體合計864.2億元的建設成本，但就指<span style=\"color: red;\">只要高鐵營運業務時獲得盈利，政府仍可從九鐵公司獲得紅利。</span><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFF<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1c57f4d97a87d5d6e5ad0ec0ae1691c1be5de1","tid":415013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩岸罵聲停不住，高鐵已過萬重山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係有方法煞停佢<br 